                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8688" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1334</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1410 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徽商期货携手肉牛产业，开启“保险+期货”新篇章</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huishang Futures collaborates with the cattle industry to embark on a new chapter of “Insurance + Futures”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吴鑫育，张珂</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徽商期货有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“保险+期货”；肉牛产业振兴；风险管理；金融衍生产品</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Insurance + futures&quot;; The cattle industry revitalization; Risk management; Financial derivatives</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农业是国民经济的基石，肉牛产业作为其重要组成部分，对农业经济和国民经济的稳定增长起着关键作用。然而，肉牛养殖户经常面临市场价格波动风险、自然灾害风险等挑战。为了应对这些风险，国家中央一号文件多次提出“保险+期货”模式，旨在通过农产品价格保险为农户提供风险分散的途径。安徽省人民政府办公厅印发了《关于实施“秸秆变肉”暨肉牛振兴计划的意见》，以期通过政策支持振兴肉牛产业，进而推动乡村振兴。徽商期货公司和安粮期货公司积极响应政策号召，联合开展了肉牛价格指数“保险+期货”项目，旨在落实政策，保障养殖户的收益，助力肉牛产业的振兴。本案例重点介绍了徽商期货在肉牛价格指数“保险+期货”项目中的发展背景、实施过程、解决的问题以及取得的成效，并探讨了未来的发展方向。通过本案例的教学，旨在帮助学习者深入理解“保险+期货”模式的创新发展思路，掌握该模式的问题解决逻辑，以便更有效地运用这一模式，推进肉牛产业的振兴和乡村振兴事业的发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Agriculture is the cornerstone of the national economy, with the cattle industry playing a vital role in its stability and growth. However, cattle farmers often face market price volatility and natural disaster risks. To mitigate these risks, the Central No. 1 Document has repeatedly proposed the &quot;Insurance + Futures&quot; model, offering a risk diversification strategy through agricultural product price insurance. The Anhui Provincial People&#39;s Government issued the &quot;Opinions on Implementing the &#39;Straw into Meat&#39; and Cattle Industry Revitalization Plan&quot;, aiming to revitalize the cattle industry and promote rural revitalization through policy support. Huishang Futures company and Anliang Futures company actively responded to the policy call and jointly launched the cattle price index &quot;Insurance + Futures&quot; project to implement policies, safeguard farmers&#39; income, and aid in the industry&#39;s revitalization. This case study focuses on the background, process, challenges, and achievements of the &quot;Insurance + Futures&quot; project in the cattle price index by Huishang Futures company, and discusses future development directions. The teaching aims to help learners deeply understand the innovative development of the &quot;Insurance + Futures&quot; model, grasp its problem-solving logic, and effectively apply this model to promote the revitalization of the cattle industry and rural development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融工程》、《金融风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">保险；期货；期权；肉牛产业风险；风险管理；“保险+期货”模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
